  <lyrics>[V1]
 Jacatatayapjjetay Tata,
 Mayjfat chuymanacajjar,
 Machak ch'amampiy phokfapjjeta,
 Kollan Ajay ch'amampi.
 
[C]
 Chuymajjan jacpanay,
 Kollan Ajayumajja;
 üca ch'amampiwa,
 Jumarojj sirviscáma.
 
[V2]
 Jacatatayapjjetay Tata,
 Ch'amamp sirviñataqui;
 Arunacamamp phokfapjjeta,
 Munañam lurafiatac.
 
[V3]
 Jacatatayapjjetay Tata,
 Kollan Ajay ch'amampi;
 lyawsafisa yapfapjjaquitay.
 Juchar atipjañatac.
 
</lyrics></song>